[{"id": 16153, "kol_id": 102, "post_id": "tw_2035923687250227296", "content": "We\u2019ve been optimizing keyboards for years.\n\nNow tools like \n@typelessdotcom\n are making them irrelevant.\n\nEven MrBeast is already there.", "likes": 4, "comments": 3, "reposts": 0, "views": 88, "bookmarks": 0, "post_url": "https://x.com/tec_aryan/status/2035923687250227296", "posted_at": "2026-03-23T03:36:47+00:00", "captured_at": "2026-03-23T04:18:06.820492+00:00", "is_notified": false, "last_likes": 4, "last_views": 88, "last_reposts": 0, "last_bookmarks": 0, "last_comments": 3, "first_captured_at": "2026-03-23T04:18:06.820492+00:00", "kol": "tec_aryan"}, {"id": 14049, "kol_id": 88, "post_id": "tw_2035826005512974416", "content": "Day 179 of the open source Asimov project is inspiring.\n\nWhat most folks fail to understand about robotics is: once the hardware is good enough, the AI brain will self iterate at record learning scale and a 2026 robot in 2029 will be mind blowing in abilities.", "likes": 98, "comments": 10, "reposts": 16, "views": 9799, "bookmarks": 7, "post_url": "https://x.com/BrianRoemmele/status/2035826005512974416", "posted_at": "2026-03-22T21:08:38+00:00", "captured_at": "2026-03-23T04:29:45.746032+00:00", "is_notified": false, "last_likes": 97, "last_views": 9758, "last_reposts": 15, "last_bookmarks": 6, "last_comments": 9, "first_captured_at": "2026-03-23T00:49:36.728364+00:00", "kol": "BrianRoemmele"}, {"id": 14970, "kol_id": 88, "post_id": "tw_2035823061392654775", "content": "A mini Bell Labs for robotics and it is not in the US.\n\nIt should be\u2014we are short term thinkers acting like the \u201cnext Facebook\u201d is on the way.\n\nIt ain\u2019t.\n\nGrandpa\u2019s era is\u2014over.\n\nBUILD BELL LABS HERE.\n\nThe Beijing Innovation Center of Humanoid Robotics:", "likes": 117, "comments": 11, "reposts": 18, "views": 9061, "bookmarks": 13, "post_url": "https://x.com/BrianRoemmele/status/2035823061392654775", "posted_at": "2026-03-22T20:56:56+00:00", "captured_at": "2026-03-23T04:29:45.746032+00:00", "is_notified": false, "last_likes": 116, "last_views": 9009, "last_reposts": 17, "last_bookmarks": 12, "last_comments": 10, "first_captured_at": "2026-03-23T02:15:51.615473+00:00", "kol": "BrianRoemmele"}, {"id": 13380, "kol_id": 88, "post_id": "tw_2035821241031135670", "content": "So good to see this!\n\n\n@beffjezos\n is the real deal and like all brilliant, does not ask permission and will not follow the fake rules of tech.\n\nHe builds and he talks about it.\n\nThis combination scares folks.\n\nInnovation taking place live right here on X:", "likes": 2, "comments": 0, "reposts": 0, "views": 84, "bookmarks": 0, "post_url": "https://x.com/BrianRoemmele/status/2035821241031135670", "posted_at": "2026-03-22T20:49:42+00:00", "captured_at": "2026-03-22T20:48:06.859091+00:00", "is_notified": false, "last_likes": 2, "last_views": 84, "last_reposts": 0, "last_bookmarks": 0, "last_comments": 0, "first_captured_at": "2026-03-22T20:48:06.859091+00:00", "kol": "BrianRoemmele"}, {"id": 13363, "kol_id": 88, "post_id": "tw_2035793986536001626", "content": "X Connectors is going to be amazing!", "likes": 29, "comments": 2, "reposts": 4, "views": 3577, "bookmarks": 3, "post_url": "https://x.com/BrianRoemmele/status/2035793986536001626", "posted_at": "2026-03-22T19:01:24+00:00", "captured_at": "2026-03-22T19:48:06.631796+00:00", "is_notified": false, "last_likes": 29, "last_views": 3577, "last_reposts": 4, "last_bookmarks": 3, "last_comments": 2, "first_captured_at": "2026-03-22T19:48:06.631796+00:00", "kol": "BrianRoemmele"}, {"id": 14806, "kol_id": 95, "post_id": "tw_2035787868107633148", "content": "11. The Polite Nudge\n\nSituation: A manager asks for a status update you provided earlier that morning.\n\nResponse: The latest status is outlined below. Let me know if you need any additional context on the design phase.\n\nWhy it works: It gracefully re-delivers the information", "likes": 8, "comments": 0, "reposts": 0, "views": 1621, "bookmarks": 7, "post_url": "https://x.com/thetripathi58/status/2035787868107633148", "posted_at": "2026-03-22T18:37:05+00:00", "captured_at": "2026-03-23T01:48:06.638165+00:00", "is_notified": false, "last_likes": 8, "last_views": 1621, "last_reposts": 0, "last_bookmarks": 7, "last_comments": 0, "first_captured_at": "2026-03-23T01:48:06.638165+00:00", "kol": "thetripathi58"}, {"id": 14145, "kol_id": 95, "post_id": "tw_2035787797701988819", "content": "5. The Fresh Start\n\nSituation: The email thread has 40 replies and the original answer is buried.\n\nResponse: Starting a fresh thread with the final approved numbers to keep things organized.\n\nWhy it works: It shows high level leadership. You recognize a messy situation and take", "likes": 13, "comments": 0, "reposts": 0, "views": 6068, "bookmarks": 8, "post_url": "https://x.com/thetripathi58/status/2035787797701988819", "posted_at": "2026-03-22T18:36:48+00:00", "captured_at": "2026-03-23T04:39:45.964758+00:00", "is_notified": false, "last_likes": 12, "last_views": 6030, "last_reposts": 0, "last_bookmarks": 8, "last_comments": 0, "first_captured_at": "2026-03-23T00:49:36.728364+00:00", "kol": "thetripathi58"}, {"id": 14146, "kol_id": 95, "post_id": "tw_2035787785836392637", "content": "4. The Clarifier\n\nSituation: A team member misunderstood a specific detail you previously outlined.\n\nResponse: To clarify my previous note, the budget is capped at 5000 dollars for this phase.\n\nWhy it works: It takes ownership of the miscommunication. Instead of blaming them for", "likes": 13, "comments": 0, "reposts": 0, "views": 8156, "bookmarks": 11, "post_url": "https://x.com/thetripathi58/status/2035787785836392637", "posted_at": "2026-03-22T18:36:45+00:00", "captured_at": "2026-03-23T04:39:45.964758+00:00", "is_notified": false, "last_likes": 12, "last_views": 8111, "last_reposts": 0, "last_bookmarks": 11, "last_comments": 0, "first_captured_at": "2026-03-23T00:49:36.728364+00:00", "kol": "thetripathi58"}, {"id": 14148, "kol_id": 95, "post_id": "tw_2035787778257240145", "content": "repo link:", "likes": 8, "comments": 0, "reposts": 0, "views": 639, "bookmarks": 7, "post_url": "https://x.com/thetripathi58/status/2035787778257240145", "posted_at": "2026-03-22T18:36:44+00:00", "captured_at": "2026-03-23T04:39:45.964758+00:00", "is_notified": false, "last_likes": 8, "last_views": 638, "last_reposts": 0, "last_bookmarks": 7, "last_comments": 0, "first_captured_at": "2026-03-23T00:49:36.728364+00:00", "kol": "thetripathi58"}, {"id": 14149, "kol_id": 95, "post_id": "tw_2035787773995843657", "content": "3. The Context Refresher\n\nSituation: A client forgot the agreed upon timeline and is asking for early delivery.\n\nResponse: To keep us on track for Friday, here is the original timeline we discussed.\n\nWhy it works: It gently enforces the boundary without being aggressive. You", "likes": 17, "comments": 0, "reposts": 0, "views": 9989, "bookmarks": 17, "post_url": "https://x.com/thetripathi58/status/2035787773995843657", "posted_at": "2026-03-22T18:36:43+00:00", "captured_at": "2026-03-23T04:39:45.964758+00:00", "is_notified": false, "last_likes": 16, "last_views": 9928, "last_reposts": 0, "last_bookmarks": 16, "last_comments": 0, "first_captured_at": "2026-03-23T00:49:36.728364+00:00", "kol": "thetripathi58"}, {"id": 14147, "kol_id": 95, "post_id": "tw_2035787766370590724", "content": "I watched a Staff Engineer open a 10GB server log in 0.3 seconds.\n\nMy VS Code had just crashed trying to do the exact same thing.\n\nHe wasn't using a supercomputer. He was using an open source editor that completely refuses to use Electron. It is called CudaText.\n\nHere are 3", "likes": 57, "comments": 9, "reposts": 31, "views": 34566, "bookmarks": 25, "post_url": "https://x.com/thetripathi58/status/2035787766370590724", "posted_at": "2026-03-22T18:36:41+00:00", "captured_at": "2026-03-23T04:39:45.964758+00:00", "is_notified": false, "last_likes": 56, "last_views": 34446, "last_reposts": 30, "last_bookmarks": 24, "last_comments": 9, "first_captured_at": "2026-03-23T00:49:36.728364+00:00", "kol": "thetripathi58"}, {"id": 14150, "kol_id": 95, "post_id": "tw_2035787762268528649", "content": "2. The Executive Summary\n\nSituation: Someone clearly did not read the long email you sent and is asking basic questions.\n\nResponse: Here are the three key takeaways from the previous update to get you up to speed.\n\nWhy it works: It acknowledges that your previous message might", "likes": 13, "comments": 0, "reposts": 0, "views": 11623, "bookmarks": 21, "post_url": "https://x.com/thetripathi58/status/2035787762268528649", "posted_at": "2026-03-22T18:36:40+00:00", "captured_at": "2026-03-23T04:39:45.964758+00:00", "is_notified": false, "last_likes": 12, "last_views": 11550, "last_reposts": 0, "last_bookmarks": 21, "last_comments": 0, "first_captured_at": "2026-03-23T00:49:36.728364+00:00", "kol": "thetripathi58"}, {"id": 14151, "kol_id": 95, "post_id": "tw_2035787750579081297", "content": "1. The Direct Resend\n\nSituation: A colleague asks for a document you already sent them yesterday.\n\nResponse: I have reattached the Q3 brief here for easy access.\n\nWhy it works: It completely removes the friction of making them dig through their inbox. You solve their immediate", "likes": 19, "comments": 0, "reposts": 0, "views": 12065, "bookmarks": 24, "post_url": "https://x.com/thetripathi58/status/2035787750579081297", "posted_at": "2026-03-22T18:36:37+00:00", "captured_at": "2026-03-23T04:39:45.964758+00:00", "is_notified": false, "last_likes": 18, "last_views": 11990, "last_reposts": 0, "last_bookmarks": 23, "last_comments": 0, "first_captured_at": "2026-03-23T00:49:36.728364+00:00", "kol": "thetripathi58"}, {"id": 14051, "kol_id": 88, "post_id": "tw_2035787611474657652", "content": "It\u2019s hard to believe it\u2019s already been 100 days since I received my Neuralink N1 implant. Looking back, the whole journey feels like science fiction that somehow became my everyday reality.\n\nThe surgery on Day 0 was surprisingly easy. A quick general anaesthetic, a small", "likes": 5815, "comments": 289, "reposts": 611, "views": 638093, "bookmarks": 563, "post_url": "https://x.com/CheckCanopy/status/2035787611474657652", "posted_at": "2026-03-22T18:36:04+00:00", "captured_at": "2026-03-23T02:00:51.080212+00:00", "is_notified": false, "last_likes": 5655, "last_views": 619694, "last_reposts": 599, "last_bookmarks": 546, "last_comments": 281, "first_captured_at": "2026-03-23T00:49:36.728364+00:00", "kol": "BrianRoemmele"}, {"id": 13361, "kol_id": 88, "post_id": "tw_2035787401550074287", "content": "BOOM!\n\nZero-Human Company Update:\n\nWe are tearing into the Tong, J. et al. paper right now:  \u201cReinforcement Learning from Community Feedback: Autonomous AI Scientists\u201d open source code!\n\nThis one is massive.\n\nThey trained a Scientific Judge on 700K high- vs. low-impact paper", "likes": 71, "comments": 9, "reposts": 20, "views": 5333, "bookmarks": 36, "post_url": "https://x.com/BrianRoemmele/status/2035787401550074287", "posted_at": "2026-03-22T18:35:14+00:00", "captured_at": "2026-03-22T19:48:06.631796+00:00", "is_notified": false, "last_likes": 71, "last_views": 5333, "last_reposts": 20, "last_bookmarks": 36, "last_comments": 9, "first_captured_at": "2026-03-22T19:48:06.631796+00:00", "kol": "BrianRoemmele"}, {"id": 13351, "kol_id": 101, "post_id": "tw_2035784712334258472", "content": "Typing is dead.\nThis just proved it.\n\nTypeless 1.0 for Windows turns your voice into action\ninstantly.\n\nNo tabs.\nNo switching.\nNo friction.\n\nYou just speak\u2026\nand it becomes clean, structured prompts across any app.\n\nFeels like your computer finally understands you.\nBuilt for:\n\n\u2022", "likes": 41, "comments": 11, "reposts": 18, "views": 4550, "bookmarks": 13, "post_url": "https://x.com/LearnWithBishal/status/2035784712334258472", "posted_at": "2026-03-22T18:24:33+00:00", "captured_at": "2026-03-23T04:18:06.820492+00:00", "is_notified": false, "last_likes": 37, "last_views": 4454, "last_reposts": 17, "last_bookmarks": 7, "last_comments": 10, "first_captured_at": "2026-03-22T19:18:07.146628+00:00", "kol": "LearnWithBishal"}, {"id": 13357, "kol_id": 97, "post_id": "tw_2035779460671180855", "content": "I filter through 100+ AI updates daily so you don't have to.  \n\nGet the 5 that actually matter:", "likes": 0, "comments": 0, "reposts": 0, "views": 787, "bookmarks": 0, "post_url": "https://x.com/heyshrutimishra/status/2035779460671180855", "posted_at": "2026-03-22T18:03:41+00:00", "captured_at": "2026-03-23T04:18:06.820492+00:00", "is_notified": false, "last_likes": 0, "last_views": 786, "last_reposts": 0, "last_bookmarks": 0, "last_comments": 0, "first_captured_at": "2026-03-22T19:48:06.631796+00:00", "kol": "heyshrutimishra"}, {"id": 13359, "kol_id": 97, "post_id": "tw_2035767635086832100", "content": "Every chip company on Earth separates its stages. Design happens in one place. Fabrication in another country. Testing somewhere else entirely. The feedback loop between those stages takes months. Sometimes years. Musk said on stage last night that what TERAFAB is doing has never", "likes": 5, "comments": 2, "reposts": 0, "views": 726, "bookmarks": 0, "post_url": "https://x.com/heyshrutimishra/status/2035767635086832100", "posted_at": "2026-03-22T17:16:41+00:00", "captured_at": "2026-03-23T04:18:06.820492+00:00", "is_notified": false, "last_likes": 5, "last_views": 725, "last_reposts": 0, "last_bookmarks": 0, "last_comments": 2, "first_captured_at": "2026-03-22T19:48:06.631796+00:00", "kol": "heyshrutimishra"}, {"id": 13795, "kol_id": 88, "post_id": "tw_2035767485518246290", "content": "Michelangelo in 1511 hid the anatomy of the human brain, which was illegal to have knowledge of in the artwork of the Sistine chapel.\n\nIt was classic hermetic encoding.", "likes": 1143, "comments": 42, "reposts": 152, "views": 47859, "bookmarks": 207, "post_url": "https://x.com/BrianRoemmele/status/2035767485518246290", "posted_at": "2026-03-22T17:16:05+00:00", "captured_at": "2026-03-23T04:49:50.364371+00:00", "is_notified": false, "last_likes": 1138, "last_views": 47743, "last_reposts": 151, "last_bookmarks": 205, "last_comments": 38, "first_captured_at": "2026-03-23T00:15:07.131467+00:00", "kol": "BrianRoemmele"}, {"id": 14050, "kol_id": 88, "post_id": "tw_2035765829199888392", "content": "A lot of artists thought\ntheir value came from labor:\n\nHours spent.\nPain endured.\nTechniques acquired.\n\nBut audiences were never paying\nfor your suffering.\n\nThey were paying for impact.\n\nAI is forcing that truth out into the open.", "likes": 127, "comments": 31, "reposts": 14, "views": 5744, "bookmarks": 9, "post_url": "https://x.com/alexutopia/status/2035765829199888392", "posted_at": "2026-03-22T17:09:31+00:00", "captured_at": "2026-03-23T03:00:51.101562+00:00", "is_notified": false, "last_likes": 126, "last_views": 5705, "last_reposts": 14, "last_bookmarks": 8, "last_comments": 31, "first_captured_at": "2026-03-23T00:49:36.728364+00:00", "kol": "BrianRoemmele"}, {"id": 13416, "kol_id": 89, "post_id": "tw_2035765552573218832", "content": "Salary won't make you rich.\n\nI've listed 70 passive income ideas to earn while you sleep.\n\n\u221eFor (Ist 500 people only).\n\nAll you need is:\n\n- Smartphone/PC\n- Internet\n- 2-4 hours a day\n\nTo get it just:\n\n1. Like & repost\n2. Comment \u201c All \u201d\n3. Follow me (so I can DM).", "likes": 30, "comments": 18, "reposts": 20, "views": 1346, "bookmarks": 15, "post_url": "https://x.com/tec_safwan/status/2035765552573218832", "posted_at": "2026-03-22T17:08:25+00:00", "captured_at": "2026-03-22T20:48:06.859091+00:00", "is_notified": false, "last_likes": 30, "last_views": 1346, "last_reposts": 20, "last_bookmarks": 15, "last_comments": 18, "first_captured_at": "2026-03-22T20:48:06.859091+00:00", "kol": "AIBuzzNews"}, {"id": 15845, "kol_id": 102, "post_id": "tw_2035758528464630143", "content": " \ud835\uddd5\ud835\udde5\ud835\u